    <description>PE - Flow created to keep fields on the Combined Funnel in sync with their counterpart on other objects. (Revenue.io Implementation Project)
12/18/23 - PE - Added fied &quot;Current Center Operating Status) to mapping.
12.22.23 - DJ - Removed first decision node for whether to update primary contacts. Added update to contact field called Revio Sequence Trigger to trigger an edit on contact records every time for sequencing. Removed field mapping to old Initial Setup Call Scheduled/Completed fields on CFs
01/08/24 - Fixed issue with BNP Webinar Status for SaaS Primary Contact
01/22/24 - PE -  If the &quot;Next Steps&quot; field is updated, check if a Onboarding Meeting call happened today and if found, perform false edit. 
01/22/24 - PE - Contacts will only get updated if a field related to them is updated (decision node).
7/18/24- JH - Added in additional BNP fields to the entry criteria and update account node to ensure data is synced between CF/account for fields used in BNP rev sequences
09/26/24 - MC - added BNP sub status fields to entry criteria and update account node</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
